query_value

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_value -  This method returns the value of a specified type of money in a certain money area.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int query_value(string type,
string where)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of money to get the value for
%^BOLD%^where%^RESET%^ - the money area the money is in
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the integer value of the money
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/money_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the value of a specified type of money in a certain
money area.
.EP

